 class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_9007551\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_9007551\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cam1731407886987.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cam1731407886987.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cam1731407886987.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cam1731407886987\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Text Highlighting automatically highlights the instances of selected or caret-based text\n\t\twithin the code editor, helping developers quickly spot relevant text and\n\t\ttokens.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cam1731407886987__ul_p23_1xy_3dc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Caret-based Highlighting:</span> When your caret is positioned on a token,\n\t\t\t\tall occurrences of that token are highlighted. This enables you to instantly see\n\t\t\t\twhere and how that token is used in the code.</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selection-based Highlighting:</span> When you select a word or phrase by\n\t\t\t\tdouble-clicking or dragging your cursor, all exact textual matches are highlighted.\n\t\t\t\tThis is particularly useful for tracking string literals, matching words, or\n\t\t\t\trepeated text in the code and comments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\">There are three properties you can configure for the Text Highlighting feature within the\n\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">SourceEdit</code> definition inside the <code class=\"ph codeph\">[widgets]</code> section\n\t\t\tin the <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file – <code class=\"ph codeph\">TextHighlight</code>,\n\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">TextHighlightMatchCase</code>, and <code class=\"ph codeph\">TextHighlightShade</code> as\n\t\t\tshown in the following example:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104cam1731407886987_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"cam1731407886987__codeblock_cx4_4yy_3dc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[widgets]\nSourceEdit=usrcedit(…;TextHighlight=on;TextHighlightMatchCase=off;TextHighlightShade=black)\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Text Higlighting Properties Description</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Property</strong></th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__2\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__3\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Default value</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">TextHighlight</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__2\">By setting <code class=\"ph codeph\">TextHighlight</code> you can switch on and off\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe Text Highlighting feature.</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__3\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">on</kbd></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">TextHighlightMatchCase</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__2\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">TextHighlightMatchCase</code> property controls whether\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe text matching for highlighting is case-sensitive.</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__3\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">off</kbd></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">TextHighlightShade</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__2\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">TextHighlightShade</code> property allows customization of the highlight\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcolor for the matching occurrences.</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cam1731407886987__table_d1n_f5d_ndc__entry__3\"><kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Black</kbd></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_9007551\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_9007551\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Text Highlighting Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Text Highlighting automatically highlights the instances of selected or caret-based text within the code editor, helping developers quickly spot relevant text and tokens. Caret-based Highlighting: When your caret is positioned on a token, all occurrences of that token are highlighted. This enables you to instantly see where and how that token is used in the code. Selection-based Highlighting: When you select a word or phrase by double-clicking or dragging your cursor, all exact textual matches are highlighted. This is particularly useful for tracking string literals, matching words, or repeated text in the code and comments. There are three properties you can configure for the Text Highlighting feature within the SourceEdit definition inside the [widgets] section in the usys.ini file – TextHighlight , TextHighlightMatchCase , and TextHighlightShade as shown in the following example: Explain this code [widgets] SourceEdit=usrcedit(…;TextHighlight=on;TextHighlightMatchCase=off;TextHighlightShade=black) Copy Table 1. Text Higlighting Properties Description Property Description Default value TextHighlight By setting TextHighlight you can switch on and off the Text Highlighting feature. on TextHighlightMatchCase The TextHighlightMatchCase property controls whether the text matching for highlighting is case-sensitive. off TextHighlightShade The TextHighlightShade property allows customization of the highlight color for the matching occurrences. Black Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}